name: 1 HOUR of Plane Spotting at PORTLAND INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT! (PDX/KPDX)
description:
Portland International Airport (PDX/KPDX) is the largest and busiest airport in the U.S. state of Oregon, and is a hub for Alaska Airlines.

It's also a joint civilian and military airport, with the Oregon Air National Guard having a base on the SE side.

I spent a few days there back in August of 2022 and filmed quite a bit of what Portland had to offer!
